%%{init: {"theme": "base", "themeVariables": {"fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono", "fontSize": "10px"}, "htmlLabels": false, "flowchart": {"htmlLabels": false}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as UCI go
    participant Search as search
    participant Root as search_root
    participant Nega as negamax
    participant TT as TT-Table
    participant Driver as search_driver
    participant Q as qsearch

    Client->>Search: search(pos, depth, limits, tt, threads)
    Search->>TT: new_search()
    Search->>Driver: iterative deepening loop
    Driver->>Root: search_root(...)
    Root->>Nega: iterate root legal moves
    loop each move
        Root->>Nega: negamax(depth-1, -beta, -alpha)
        Nega->>TT: probe(hash)
        alt depth == 0
            Nega->>Q: qsearch(...)
            Q->>Q: stand pat plus capture search
        else depth > 0
            Nega->>Nega: generate moves + static eval
            Nega->>TT: store(best move, score, depth, flag)
        end
    end
    Root-->>Driver: best move at depth d
    Driver-->>Search: final SearchInfo
    Search-->>Client: bestmove uci_move
